The Kitui government has hired 2,156 nursery school teachers under an annual budget of Sh260 million. A report from Kitui Governor Julius Malombe&rsquo;s office on efforts made to modernise ECDE says the county has also built classrooms.&ldquo;Modern classrooms are fast replacing grass-thatch mud houses or trees for classrooms. We&rsquo;ve build 501 new ECDE classrooms across the county and rehabilitated five others,&rdquo; it says.